# Protect Main Branch

Before new work starts, make sure the checked-in ruleset is active on GitHub.

## Requirement

The `main` branch must have the `Protect main` ruleset applied:
- Block branch deletion
- Block force pushes
- Require pull requests before merge
- Require `test` and `e2e-website` to pass

## Workflow

1. Run `./.github/scripts/sync_main_ruleset.sh`
2. Verify `gh api repos/jimmymalhan/systemdesignlaws.xyz/rulesets --jq '.[].name'` includes `Protect main`
3. Never push directly to `main`
